{"title":"土葬习俗一瞥","authors":["林洁"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":12,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"土葬习俗一瞥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林洁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唢呐、锣和鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引领着披黑纱的葬歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缓缓而来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵幡在风里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"零乱飞舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各色纸张制扎成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪做的悲痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把遗风召示"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那哭不叫哭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是用唱来表示或真或假的哀痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭诉过去的那人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭诉过去的那事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭，最好的效果是惊叹四起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而棺后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"簇拥着哀歌和沉默——走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走了几千几百年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路纸钱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒做慷慨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有香烛又有祭品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都熏成祖传的礼乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而鞭炮爆响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不知为多少人悲鸣——走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走了几千几百年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去了，去了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缓缓而去，缓缓而去"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}